flowchart TD
    Input[User Input] --> Intent[Intent Classification]
    Intent --> Context[Retrieve Memory + Knowledge]
    Context --> Policy[Apply Persona + Tool Policy]
    Policy --> Plan[Plan]
    Plan --> NeedTool{Need Tool?}
    NeedTool -->|No| Generate[Generate Response]
    NeedTool -->|Yes| ToolRequest[Tool Request]
    ToolRequest --> Gateway[Tool Gateway]
    Gateway --> Provenance[Provenance / Injection Check]
    Provenance --> PolicyEngine[Policy Engine - policy_rules + trust_score]
    PolicyEngine --> Approval{allow / ask / deny}
    Approval -->|ask| AskBob[Ask Bob]
    AskBob --> Decision{Approved?}
    Decision -->|No| Abort[Abort/Explain]
    Decision -->|Yes| RiskCheck{High-risk tool type?}
    Approval -->|deny| Abort
    Approval -->|allow| RiskCheck
    RiskCheck -->|Yes| Sandbox[Execute in Ephemeral Sandbox]
    RiskCheck -->|No| Execute[Execute Tool]
    Sandbox --> Observe[Observe Result]
    Execute --> Observe[Observe Result]
    Observe --> Generate
    Generate --> Trace[Trace + Audit]
    Trace --> MemoryCandidate[Extract Memory Candidates]
    MemoryCandidate --> Output[Final Output]
